body_html:
I have the same error following the instructions at https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_windows. After reverting back to:
pip install --upgrade https://storage.googleapis.com/tensorflow/windows/gpu/tensorflow_gpu-1.0.0-cp35-cp35m-win_amd64.whl the issue is resolved.
